{"tid":771444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人民日報：蘋果需要與中國人民分享發展紅利","createTime":"2018-08-08T03:17:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T05:49:50.000Z","uid":39464,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"5c695a801b5303190a24820b38a69ac03085b640","tid":771444,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T03:17:59.000Z","msg":"中美貿易戰之下，以出口貨值計中國並無談判的籌碼，因而以不同方式應對。繼環球時報後，人民日報亦稱，蘋果公司在中國強勁的銷售表現，讓中國在與美國持續貿易爭端中擁有談判的籌碼。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，中國是迄今為止蘋果公司最重要的海外市場，如果蘋果成為中國人民憤怒和民族主義情緒的目標，蘋果將面臨風險。儘管中美之間存在貿易沖突，中國並不希望向蘋果關閉大門，但是如果蘋果希望在中國賺大錢的話，它需要與中國人民分享發展紅利(the company needs to do more to share the economic cake with local Chinese people)。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，特朗普政府挑起的貿易沖突提醒中國重新審視中美貿易。在中國經營的美國公司看來是中美貿易的最大贏家。中國市場對許多頂級美國品牌來說至關重要，這讓中國政府在貿易爭端中採取強硬立場有了更多回旋餘地。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1533694955516&amp;issue=20180808\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1533694955516%26issue%3D20180808&d=Gwu7UGslcp1keCAvSO4gUJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=e74f31d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1533694955516%26issue%3D20180808&h=706b127c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1533694955516&amp;issue=20180808</a>"},{"pid":"37660746d5c65be9794c65e2becf4007d7aef0a2","tid":771444,"uid":28765,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T03:19:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.9words.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/120912152824a90ea7de51ef63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.9words.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F01%2F120912152824a90ea7de51ef63.jpg&h=de4f2bfd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14b46c5a41a00d57d19a29fa7f26f73cd59cf534","tid":771444,"uid":43718,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"37660746d5c65be9794c65e2becf4007d7aef0a2","tid":771444,"uid":28765,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score"